ral mechanistic model for admixture histories of hybrid populations verdu p rosenberg na genetics 2011 189 4 1413 26 consistency properties of species tree inference by minimizing deep coalescences than cv rosenberg na j comput biol 2011 18 1 1 15 view all 10 you are here home faculty navigation for this section department of biology education & training courses faculty research sites about us contact us search profiles by name help community academic profiles stanford only login update your profile connect with colleagues find a researcher profiles by name profiles by department profiles by program help go stanford only login update your profile connect with colleagues site navigation home faculty education & training biology events giving to biology stanford medicine resources stanford medicine getting care overview find a physician find a clinical care center stanford hospital & clinics lucile packard children's hospital emergency research overview school of medicine news & resources clinical trials departments institutes & centers faculty profiles education & training overview school of medicine programs admissions continuing medical education alumni lane medical library community overview stanford health library community newsletter volunteering public service & community partnerships renewal & new building projects about us overview news careers ways to give find a person contact us maps & directions the dean's newsletter stanford university biology footer stanford university department of biology gilbert hall stanford california 94305 4200 phone 650 723 2413 fax 650 723 6132 terms of use copyright complaints 2009 stanford school of medicine terms of use powered by irt
